From: Devesh Sharma <devesh.sharma@broadcom.com>
Date: Sat, 15 Feb 2020 12:10:59 -0500
Subject: RDMA/bnxt_re: Replace chip context structure with pointer
Patch-mainline: v5.7-rc1
Git-commit: 0cfb329db988804124423b311a2845e56914e3ca
